title: 729. Takeaways from Bills vs. Titans Game & Teams Who Could Have A New QB Next Season
itunes:title: 729. Takeaways from Bills vs. Titans Game & Teams Who Could Have A New QB Next Season
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. On this special show, the guys start by giving their takeaways from the Buffalo Bills and Tennessee Titans game, while also analyzing some of the top AFC teams. Then, the duo look at teams who could potentially have a new quarterback next season. To wrap up the show, the pair discuss college football and break down the players on Georgia's defense.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
